keyFacts: The document is a delayed response from the NYS Division of Criminal Justice Services to an FBI inquiry.
The response is related to a search request based on identifier END 171.
Michael C. Green is identified as the Executive Deputy Commissioner of the responding agency.
The document is dated October 6, 2021, indicating ongoing investigative activity related to the Epstein case at that time.
